node.text:
Summer days in Capri, Italy 💚
TAG someone who needs to visit Capri! 🇮🇹
Video by: @terplanet

Dinner and one of the best views at Ristorante Hotel Grotta Palazzese in Puglia, Italy. It is located in a natural cave and the sitting area has views overlooking the sea. Perfect for a romantic dinner. 🌊
Slide 1: @danielafilomeno 
Slide 2: @terplanet 
Slide 3: @noemiedoardi 
Slide 4: @pinkines 
Slide 5: @angie.garner 
Slide 6: @sophieelkus
Slide 7: @giselle_e

node.text:
WIN A HOLIDAY TO PARADISE! 😱🌴☀️

We've teamed up with our besties at @isawitfirst and @lullabellzuk to give you the chance to PICK YOUR ISLAND PARADISE and choose out of 4 dream island destinations 💖PLUS £250 vouchers from @isawitfirst and @lullabellzuk 🙌 To enter, you MUST:

✈️To enter, you must:

✨FOLLOW @trendingtravel.co.uk @isawitfirst and @lullabellzuk

✨LIKE this post

✨ TAG a best friend you would take with you!!

DON’T FORGET it’s unlimited entries… go go go!👀🙌

The competition closes at 23:59 on 10/08/21⏱

Please be aware of fake accounts trying to contact you during the competition. This is our only official page and the winner will be announced via our story at 12:00 on 11/08/21. T&C’s will be available at trendingtravel.co.uk/competition
